              <span id="reviewTextContainer3235805289" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17691347850641135533">The Singing Sword in the Eagle Series by Jack Whyte is an excellent second book in this saga about Camelot. This book gets a little racy in places, but the overall story moves forward. If you enjoyed the<br/>first book in the series The Skystone, then you will enjoy this one too. Lots of surprises at the end of the book for the future!</span>

